		"description": {
			"value": "<p><em>Wondrous Item - Uncommon</em></p><p><em>This robe is covered with cloth patches of various shapes and colors.</em></p><p><em>A magic item like this grants a bonus to checks where relevant and counts as magical for overcoming effects.</em></p><p><strong>Action</strong></p><ul><li><p>Detach a patch to create the object or creature it depicts. Once the last patch is removed, the robe becomes an ordinary garment.</p></li></ul><p><strong>Patches</strong></p><ul><li><p>Two each: @UUID[Compendium.dnd5e.equipment24.Item.KZUoiZrigDbovEu7]{Bullseye Lantern} (filled and lit), @UUID[Compendium.dnd5e.equipment24.Item.phbwepDagger0000]{Dagger}, @UUID[Compendium.dnd5e.equipment24.Item.phbagMirror00000]{Mirror}, @UUID[Compendium.dnd5e.equipment24.Item.phbagPole0000000]{Pole}, @UUID[Compendium.dnd5e.equipment24.Item.x8jC9e00t4cUYiKR]{Rope} (coiled), @UUID[Compendium.dnd5e.equipment24.Item.phbagSack0000000]{Sack}.</p></li><li><p>Plus [[/r 4d4]] additional patches (roll or choose from the table below).</p></li></ul><details><summary>Table</summary><p>@Embed[Compendium.dnd5e.tables24.RollTable.dmgRobeOfUsefulI rollable]</p></details><section id=\"foundry-secret-1\" class=\"secret\"><p><strong>Foundry Note</strong></p><p>Activities for the guaranteed patches include limited uses for tracking; duplicate/rename them for rolled patches as needed.</p></section>",
